  "title": "Site Engineer (fresh grad)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></p><p>Main Duties:</p><ul><li>Oversee the construction activities and progress, plan, implement and monitor work</li><li>Schedule in accordance to the master and detailed work program</li><li>Liaise with Professional Engineer on the Temporary works</li><li>Liaise with consultants (QPS) for technical issues and coordinate the site activities with subcontractors</li><li>Handle of technical and engineering problems</li><li>Provide guidance to supervisors in relation to construction works, ensure progress according to schedule,</li><li>Maintain quality standards, carry out site inspections and resolve technical issues on time</li><li>Prepare report and method statement whenever necessary</li><li>Manage and control workers and monitor their work closely to keep site safer and neat</li><li>Supervise ongoing site activities closely</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Degree in Civil Engineering or equivalent</li><li>Open to fresh grads</li><li>6.0 days work-week and must be committed to work overtime when needs arise.</li></ul>",
